title: Orange cream cheese date squares
ingredients: ['Date squares', '150g caster sugar', '115g butter, softened', '120ml water', '225g pitted chopped dates', '155g plain flour', '3/4 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '4 tablespoons orange juice', '180ml milk', '2 eggs', '1 tablespoon orange zest', '110g chopped pecans', 'Icing', '360g icing sugar', '75g butter, softened', '85g cream cheese, softened', '1 tablespoon orange zest', '2 1/2 tablespoons orange juice']
